{\footnotesize\textbf{plotSimulationDatasetCircle}}

\begin{par}
Plot circular path of Hx, Hy and Vcos, Vsin at each sensor array position. Normed to max overall array positions and normed to max at each array position.
\end{par} \vspace{1em}
